\SE[1] Today, we will conduct a team competition among
the top 8 members. \SE[3] It will test their ability,
coordination, and strategy... It is an examination that will
challenge their overall capabilities. \SE[1] As you know,
the scoring is also high. Each of you, please do your best.

Number Eightman: Strategy, huh...? What should we do...? I'm
not good at this kind of thing...

Eighth Member: Honestly, I don't think we have any choice.
After all, Lunaroa is too far ahead.

Eighth Member: It's a template, but... Lunaroa, please focus
on attacking. I will gradually recover the areas that need
care... Goban and Eightman, please cover Lunaroa... So, how
does that sound?

[5] Goban: I'll be fine with that...! I think I can defend
the basics properly.

Oh, I'm fine with that...! I don't really understand it well
though...!

\SM[nod]\SE[15]Let's relax and do this.
\SM[nod]\SE[15]It's okay. We can do it.

\SE[3]This is also a test to confirm your achievements. Show
me your grown-up selves. \SE[25]That's all from me.
\SE[25]...Well then.
\SE[1]It seems like everyone is ready. Let's begin.
